metadata.name: Legacy
metadata.description:
This is the first ever collaboration between Grondin (https://twitter.com/grondin506) and Farshid Feyzi (https://twitter.com/farshidfeyzi64). This signed piece is original and a unique 1:1 artwork.

In this portrait you can see my daughter holding my first ever film camera. She is now the proud owner of my Canon AE-1.
